    "body" : "\n\n<p>Hide it for all activities using the theme</p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>&lt;style name=\"MyTheme\" parent=\"Theme\"&gt;\n    &lt;item name=\"android:windowSoftInputMode\"&gt;stateHidden&lt;/item&gt;\n&lt;/style&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>set the theme</p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>&lt;application android:theme=\"@style/MyTheme\"&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
