    "answer_id" : 51104691,
    "question_id" : 9732761,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To expand upon the accepted answer by @Lucas:</p>\n\n<p>Call this from your activity in one of the early life cycle events:</p>\n\n<p><code>getWindow().setSoftInputMode(WindowManager.LayoutParams.SOFT_INPUT_STATE_HIDDEN);</code></p>\n\n<h2>Kotlin Example:</h2>\n\n<pre><code>override fun onResume() {\n  super.onResume()\n\n  window.setSoftInputMode(WindowManager.LayoutParams.SOFT_INPUT_STATE_HIDDEN)\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
