    "answer_id" : 51764114,
    "question_id" : 9732761,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just add this in your manifest.xml file</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;activity android:name=\".MainActivity\"\n            android:windowSoftInputMode=\"stateHidden\"&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You are all done.</p>\n"
